Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.90,0:12:42.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 所以他才會讓總選舉制度復活
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.82,0:12:45.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,推選出新的Center Nova
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.26,0:12:48.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能夠幫助大家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.90,0:12:52.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果有人成為Center Nova的話
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.22,0:12:55.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就可以救出優子姐嗎
