Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.60,0:18:09.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逃跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.76,0:18:12.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說不定是把我們的消息報告給DES
